---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Sponsors from "../components/sections/Sponsors.astro";
import Services from "../components/sections/Services.astro";
---
<MainLayout
  title="Software company in London where software permeates everything we do. We believe the most interesting questions come from real world problems."
  description="Our Laravel agency website offers access to the largest software tools pool in the world created by developers for developers."
>
  <main class="space-y-28">
    <!-- Agency Info Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white text-center">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900" title="Laravel Software Development Agency">
          <span class="text-red-600">Laravel™</span> Services
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-6">
          We are a <strong>Laravel™</strong> -exclusive software agency</strong> offering <strong>custom Laravel™ development services</strong>,
          ongoing Laravel™ support, and expert Laravel™ consulting.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">
          We’ve built <strong>ready-to-use Laravel™ starter kits</strong> for 15+ software categories — including eCommerce, CRM, CMS, Project Management, and more.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-gray-600">
          Whether you're starting from scratch or modernising legacy software,
          our Laravel™ starter kits and tools help you launch faster and scale smarter.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Services />
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative from-blue-50 to-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-28">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left space-y-8">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900" title="Laravel Development Services">
              <span class="text-red-600">Laravel™</span> Impossible? Let’s see.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-2xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Laravel™ Agency strives to continuously progress Laravel™, by sharing our latest developments and best practices.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our team tries to improve the state of Laravel™ through research, systems engineering, and collaboration across the globe.
              We publish hundreds of Laravel™ author-written papers each year across a wide range of domains,
              sharing our latest developments in order to collaboratively progress computing and science.
            </p>
            <p>
              Using skill, experience and client input we create powerful,
              valuable solutions that stand the test of time. Our Laravel™
              development services combine these foundations with technical
              prowess, flawless design and an integrated approach.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="md:w-1/2 mt-12 md:mt-0">
            <img
              src="logo.png"
              alt="Laravel software development agency"
              class="w-full h-auto animate-float"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Starter Kits Section -->
    <section id="starter-kits" class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Pre-Built Laravel™ Solutions for Rapid Development
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Accelerate your time-to-market with our battle-tested Laravel™ starter kits:
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">eCommerce Solutions</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>✅ Shopify/Magento migration kits</li>
            <li>✅ PCI-compliant checkout systems</li>
            <li>✅ Inventory management modules</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Business Automation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>✅ CRM/ERP integration packages</li>
            <li>✅ Workflow automation engines</li>
            <li>✅ API gateway configurations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Enterprise Features</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>✅ SSO authentication systems</li>
            <li>✅ Audit logging frameworks</li>
            <li>✅ Role-based access controls</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Starter Kits Categories Section -->
    <section id="starter-kits-categories" class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 title="Laravel Starter Kits for Every Software Category" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Laravel Starter Kits for Every Software Category
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          We’ve developed production-ready starter kits for every type of Laravel app:
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-gray-700">
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li>✅ <strong>Miscellaneous</strong></li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Project Management Tools</strong><br />Track tasks, milestones, budgets with Kanban boards.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Help and Support Tools</strong><br />Ticketing systems, live chat, knowledge bases.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Shopping Carts</strong><br />Full eCommerce features: variations, coupons, payment gateways.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Social Networking</strong><br />Messaging, profiles, activity feeds, followers.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Images and Media</strong><br />Galleries, uploads, watermarks, responsive previews.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Forms</strong><br />Dynamic form builders with validation and exportable submissions.</li>
        </ul>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li>✅ <strong>Loaders and Uploaders</strong><br />Drag-and-drop uploads, progress tracking, background workers.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Calendars</strong><br />Scheduling events, reminders, collaborative calendars.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Database Abstractions</strong><br />DTOs, ORM mappings, database tools.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Search</strong><br />Advanced search with indexing and filtering.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Ratings and Charts</strong><br />User feedback, star ratings, data visualizations.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Navigation</strong><br />Dynamic menu builders, breadcrumbs, mega menus.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Countdowns</strong><br />Timers for product launches, webinars, sales events.</li>
        </ul>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li>✅ <strong>News Tickers</strong><br />Real-time updates for news, notifications, blog feeds.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Polls</strong><br />Interactive voting systems with real-time results.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Laravel Partners</strong><br />Find a Laravel Partner for expert guidance and project support.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Laravel Agency Website</strong><br />Database of trusted developers and studios for collaboration.</li>
          <li>✅ <strong>Large Software Tools Pool</strong><br />Massive collection of starter kits created by developers, for developers.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-20">
        Already have a brilliant idea brewing in your mind, or maybe a project that's hitting roadblocks?
        Whether you're building the next unicorn SaaS, upgrading an old dusty legacy system, or just wanna optimise your current Laravel stack, we're your ride or die, fam.
        <br /><br />
        <b>Our Laravel services</b> are designed for businesses who think beyond the basics — because today, slow, buggy apps are just not it. 🚫
        <br /><br />
        <b>🔧 Full Custom Laravel Builds</b> — Whether it's MVPs or Enterprise-grade portals, we deliver production-ready apps with layered architecture, modular design, and TDD practices. Никакой монолитной каши. Только чистый, расширяемый код.
        <br /><br />
        <b>⚙️ API Integrations</b> — Connect your Laravel backend with third-party services like Stripe, PayPal, Twilio, Firebase, AWS, and beyond. Need custom webhooks, OAuth2 integrations, or event-driven microservices? It's our playground. 😎
        <br /><br />
        <b>🚀 Performance Optimization</b> — Who wants a slow website? No one. Мы оптимизируем SQL запросы, настраиваем Redis, Horizon, и строим асинхронные очереди для мгновенной обработки данных.
        <br /><br />
        <b>🛡️ Security Hardening</b> — Laravel security is 🔥 out of the box, but layered security? Even better. 从CSRF保护到API加密，我们让你的应用坚不可摧。
        <br /><br />
        <b>🎯 Strategic Consulting</b> — Tech debt, bad architecture, slow releases? If your Laravel app’s growth is stuck, we provide detailed roadmaps, hands-on code reviews, and CTO-level guidance to future-proof your platform. 由经验丰富的开发人员直接提供支持。
        <br /><br />
        <b>🌐 Multi-Tenant SaaS</b> — Building a platform that hosts multiple businesses under one roof? Multi-tenancy is tricky af if done wrong. Мы используем проверенные паттерны и современные библиотеки для изоляции данных и масштабируемости.
        <br /><br />
        <b>🛠️ DevOps Automation</b> — Build pipelines, deploy zero-downtime updates, auto-scale your services. Manual FTP uploads are dead, fam. CICD (Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment) or bust. 💥
        <br /><br />
        <b>🧠 AI and Laravel</b> — Machine Learning models, LLM APIs, intelligent agents? Bring the AI sauce to your Laravel app without making a mess. 我们可以帮助您整合OpenAI, Ollama, Langchain, 和更多。
        <br /><br />
        **And the best bit?** Everything is built around **SOLID**, **KISS**, and **DRY** principles, meaning you’re getting a future-proof, easy-to-maintain codebase that your next dev team will actually thank you for. No spaghetti, no headaches.
        <br /><br />
        <b>Let's be real: Laravel is evolving crazy fast</b> — and so are user expectations. 
        Old-school PHP apps? 💤 Dead.
        Static HTML? Cute but nah.
        Modern apps need fast APIs, slick UX, real-time updates, and auto-scaling infra.  
        И если вы выберете нас, то получите больше, чем просто кодеров — получите партнеров по росту. 🚀
      </p>
    </section>

    <Sponsors />
    
  </main>
</MainLayout>
